Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.13,0:00:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.21,0:00:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.15,0:00:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候 怎么说 很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.64,0:00:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.38,0:00:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在摸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.65,0:00:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边口交一边自找介绍吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.93,0:01:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.34,0:01:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就做这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.42,0:01:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是结衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.70,0:01:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.57,0:01:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.71,0:01:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是结衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.05,0:02:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才要射了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了的话做不了自我介绍哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是什么\N三围？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上面开始88 59 89
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.69,0:02:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在练习游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有参加补习社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了吗\N不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.41,0:03:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住这个了话就可以射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我介绍还没完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能表示出你很淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以射了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.54,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我会射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.97,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.99,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 要射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你射的\N都说不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍一下换衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你运动神经应该不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在参加补习社吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次教我国语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你擅长国语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了\N都叫你忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要加速啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你忍住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来打算是慢慢来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却那么淫荡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.02,0:07:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算慢点做的没想到你会射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.36,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中听到悲鸣了吧\N说求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.96,0:07:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但B说了去旅馆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没什么了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里拍哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.52,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想继续做下去\N却做不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.65,0:07:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30秒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是30秒\N我觉得已经很厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次慢点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.82,0:08:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么淫荡喜欢恶作剧的姐姐\N契机是某个旅馆发生的事情..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.24,0:11:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专业比赛用泳衣\N中出教练!湿滑滑的按摩液性爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:12:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专业比赛用泳衣\N中出教练!湿滑滑的按摩液性爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.66,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是..几个星期前的旅馆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说\N没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.14,0:12:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你成为教练作为工作的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 平时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是秘密\N其实我是补习社的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在教导国语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是老师吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.24,0:13:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说\N是一间小的补习社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生也只是中学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.66,0:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会很失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.47,0:13:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是老师的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.07,0:13:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门去教中学生的学习吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的工作活动的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.36,0:14:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生的时候有练习过游泳\N对游泳比较有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.78,0:14:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方是会员制的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.72,0:14:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想能不能因为工作的原因进去\N虽然有点不谨慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是补习社的话有点做不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.55,0:14:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是像你这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.03,0:15:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想采用你做教练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立马就想采用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.44,0:15:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真话这种会员制的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有地位的人才能进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说出这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.39,0:15:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让你工作\N有被邀请过做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.13,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人都是很绅士的人\N不会有这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.54,0:15:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教练工作应该都是泳衣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛用的泳衣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是那种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.82,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能强调出身体的曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有被邀请过去做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样 大家都..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.17,0:16:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只是聊聊天而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有男朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.32,0:16:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没有\N交不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.06,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的\N在补习社也没有邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.41,0:16:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补习社绝对有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中事生都会说老师真漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N人家都是普通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.15,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳的也是很绅士的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不会发生什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.44,0:17:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.71,0:17:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结衣你那么性感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.18,0:17:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有很多人注视着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.73,0:17:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是个美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.61,0:18:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有人在想象你的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.22,0:18:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得今天来了\N都认识了彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以换这件衣服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.57,0:18:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N等这件衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都等着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里穿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.31,0:18:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.98,0:18:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就一直想象着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会转过去不看的
